text: Lycée des métiers Hélène Boucher is a vocational senior high school in Tremblay-en-France, Seine-Saint-Denis, France, in the Paris metropolitan area. In August 2016 a riot broke out outside of the high school. ==References== ==External links== * Lycée Hélène Boucher Category:Lycées in Seine-Saint-Denis
